                {q: "Given the data for the reaction A + B → C, determine the order of the reaction with respect to each reactant.\n[A]=0.10, [B]=0.20, Rate=6.80×10⁻⁵\n[A]=0.10, [B]=0.40, Rate=2.72×10⁻⁴\n[A]=0.20, [B]=0.40, Rate=5.44×10⁻⁴", opts: ["The reaction is first-order with respect to A and first-order with respect to B", "The reaction is first-order with respect to A and second-order with respect to B", "The reaction is second-order with respect to A and first-order with respect to B", "The reaction is fourth-order with respect to A and first-order with respect to B", "zero order with respect to A and one-half order with respect to B"], ans: "B"},
