                {q: "When the half-equation is balanced correctly using the smallest coefficients, how many electrons, and on which side, are needed to balance the following half-reaction?\nBr₂(l) → Br⁻(aq)", opts: ["three electrons on the reactant side", "three electrons on the product side", "one electron on the product side", "two electrons on the reactant side", "two electrons on the product side"], ans: "D"},
